{"tid":2141685,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"電子遊戲世界中的香港建築","createTime":"2020-08-06T01:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T02:21:24.000Z","uid":321748,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a6880ab93810d559e8093ae51e2e4bb5cc62c4d","tid":2141685,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T01:37:00.000Z","msg":"儘管香港本地電子遊戲開發者的數目相對較少，但香港卻出現在全球逾150個電子遊戲中，數量之多令人驚訝。這些遊戲呈現香港的不同面貌，從九龍城寨的懷舊場景，到數碼龐克風格的未來派畫面，不一而足。但是，為甚麼香港會如此頻繁地出現在電子遊戲中？而當中所呈現的面貌又有多符合真實的城市場景？戴修在這次研究分享中討論所謂「遊戲世紀」及「亞洲世紀」的交會，探索香港在電子遊戲中的多種面貌，並從中揭示這個城市作為世界樞紐及文化物品不同涵義。<br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.mplus.org.hk/tc/talks/hong-kong-architecture-in-the-video-game-vernacular/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.mplus.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftalks%2Fhong-kong-architecture-in-the-video-game-vernacular%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F7YQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=79fb1917\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.mplus.org.hk/tc/talks/hong-kong-architecture-in-the-video-game-vernacular/</a>"},{"pid":"6c5c9fcde34b32bebf08f9779cf1a7676d57172e","tid":2141685,"uid":303599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T02:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b73d973641dd36a8c1d6307ea830482961d3b6f","tid":2141685,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T02:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ba2b8622a8344febf102efefcf088a4dc6cfa4","tid":2141685,"uid":24682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T20:32:56.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec998469226f54350530f5177ef399616e7bb31","tid":2141685,"uid":361703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T20:43:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a7796cacda5bc8a16aa2e5947353f17f7b60aca","tid":2141685,"uid":55096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit